text: Jing Xiao is a robotics professor at WPI. Xiao was named a Fellow of the Institute of Electrical and Electronics Engineers (IEEE) in 2013 for her contributions to robot compliant motion and haptic interaction. == References == Category:Fellow Members of the IEEE Category:Living people Category:University of North Carolina at Charlotte faculty Category:21st- century American engineers Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
